trans-unit.source: OpenID Provider Configuration URI : JSON document with OpenID Provider Configuration Information (usually https://{provider}/.well-known/openid-configuration)
Get param name for jwt : $_GET param, which holds the 'jwt' token
Storage users folder UID : Storage system folder, where all new cognito users will be saved locally
User group UID : User group for all newly created local cognito users
Priority : The priority is used to define a call order for services. The service with the highest priority is called first. The default range is 0-100.
Quality : Among services with the same priority, the service with the highest quality, but the same priority will be preferred. The default range is 0-100.
